<p>
<note n="0121001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0121001">本文 Sākyaputtā 是 Sākyaputtiyā（or Sākyaputti）？</note>
<note n="0121002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0121002">本文 Māyādevī ca 是 Māyādevī vā？</note>
<note n="0122003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0122003">本文 Hema 是 Hemā？</note>
<note n="0122004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0122004">本文 vinaya pañca 是 nikāye pañca。</note>
<note n="0122005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0122005">本文 sujātā kulaputtena 是 pūjitā kulaputtenā？</note>
<note n="0123006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0123006">本文 sabbapāpikā 是 sabbāpalikā？</note>
<note n="0123007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0123007">本文 sabbapāli 是 sabbapālī？</note>
<note n="0123008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0123008">apagate bhaye 依字義去危險時。</note>
<note n="0123009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0123009">本文 pasādika Jambudīpā sāsanena bahū janā 是 pasāditā Jambudīpe sāsanena bahū jane？</note>
<note n="0124010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0124010">本文 vibhajjavādi 是 vibhajjavādi？</note>
<note n="0125011" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0125011">Nāgaraṅgaṇa 於阿<g ref="#CB00145">㝹</g>羅陀市之東（大王統史二十一．二）。</note>
<note n="0125012" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0125012">陀眉羅（Damila Skt. Dravida）所謂南印度境吒羅奇陀之（達羅毘荼）。</note>
<note n="0125013" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0125013">大王統史二十一．八參照。</note>
<note n="0125014" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0125014">（Mahāvāra）之原語，可譯為大品？或譯為大事件？</note>
</p>
